%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20has%20introduced%20new%20export%20controls%20on%20China's%20semiconductor%20industry%2C%20targeting%20140%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20aims%20to%20curb%20China's%20AI%20and%20defense%20tech%20growth%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20previously%20billed%20China%20as%20the%20main%20threat%20to%20the%20US%20AI%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20announced%20another%20round%20of%20export%20controls%20on%20China's%20semiconductor%20industry%20on%20Monday%2C%20multiple%20outlets%20reported%2C%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20term.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-biden-china-curbs-stocks-chip-suppliers-asml-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestrict%20exports%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20140%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20including%20chip%20equipment%20heavyweight%20Naura%20Technology%20Group%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20curb%20China's%20growing%20capabilities%20in%20AI%20and%20defense%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20third%20crackdown%20the%20US%20has%20initiated%20on%20China's%20chipmaking%20industry%20since%20October%202022.%20The%20move%20will%20also%20stop%20the%20export%20of%20advanced%20high-bandwidth%20memory%2C%20a%20key%20component%20used%20in%20developing%20AI%20chips%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChip%20manufacturers%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20International%20Corporation%20and%20Huawei%20are%20also%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20140%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20the%20strongest%20controls%20ever%20enacted%20by%20the%20US%20to%20degrade%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China's%20ability%20to%20make%20the%20most%20advanced%20chips%20that%20they're%20using%20in%20their%20military%20modernization%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cspan%3EGina%20Raimondo%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20US%20commerce%20secretary%2C%20told%20reporters%20from%20the%20Financial%20Times%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20and%20others%2C%20on%20Sunday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20long%20been%20embroiled%20in%20a%20technological%20race%20against%20China%2C%20which%20is%20making%20developments%20in%20AI%20and%20military%20tech%20at%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration's%20latest%20sanctions%20are%20partly%20driven%20by%20national%20security%20concerns%20that%20China's%20access%20to%20high-quality%20chips%20could%20allow%20it%20to%20bolster%20its%20military%20applications%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20use%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fchinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20researchers%20in%20China%20affiliated%20with%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20had%20used%20Meta's%20open-source%20AI%20model%20Llama%20to%20develop%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20could%20be%20applied%20to%20potential%20military%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20the%20latest%20wave%20of%20measures%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20Beijing%20reportedly%20anticipates%20further%20sanctions%20from%20Trump.%20China%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20stockpile%20chips%20from%20the%20US%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20purchases%20reaching%20%241.11%20billion%20in%20October%2C%20according%20to%20customs%20data%20analyzed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Feconomy%2Fchina-economy%2Farticle%2F3287571%2Fchina-races-stockpile-us-chips-trump-ramps-sanctions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevious%20comments%20from%20Trump%20suggest%20he%20is%20aligned%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20thwarting%20China's%20AI%20growth.%20In%20a%20June%20interview%20with%20social%20media%20personality%20Logan%20Paul%2C%20Trump%20billed%20China%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20threat%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US%20AI%20industry.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20some%20internal%20disagreements%20about%20the%20approach%20to%20restricting%20Hauwei%20chip%20production%20facilities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F2334d3d9-d744-4d1f-94cc-e328968b41ce%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20of%20the%20Chinese%20tech%20giant's%20chip%20production%20plants%20were%20not%20included%20on%20the%20list%2C%20with%20one%20person%20close%20to%20the%20discussions%20telling%20the%20FT%20that%20they%20were%20not%20in%20operation%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20clear%20if%20they%20would%20be%20used%20for%20the%20production%20of%20advanced%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMao%20Ning%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20%26quot%3BChina%20is%20firmly%20opposed%20to%20the%20US%20overstretching%20the%20concept%20of%20national%20security%2C%20abusing%20export%20control%20measures%2C%20and%20making%20malicious%20attempts%20to%20block%20and%20suppress%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-us-export-controls-china-tech-ai-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733146560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674dab8ae45a68623a275ef1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-us-export-controls-china-tech-ai-2024