ther%20was%20the%20Vice%20President%20and%20then%20President%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20DEPARTMENT%20OF%20JUSTICE%20WEAPONISED%20FOR%20FOREIGN%20POLICY%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20faces%20criticism%20about%20being%20weaponised%20against%20political%20opponents%20in%20the%20US%20and%20also%20misused%20for%20foreign%20policy%20that%20benefitted%20those%20in%20power.%20Geopolitical%20experts%20and%20former%20diplomats%20have%20highlighted%20how%20Hunter%20Biden%20used%20his%20father's%20political%20clout%20to%20gain%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20China%20and%20how%20the%20US%20foreign%20policy%20was%20reportedly%20moulded%20by%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20to%20suit%20such%20personal%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20grants%20'unconditional'%20pardon%20to%20son%20Hunter%20Biden%20in%20federal%20convictions%3B%20Experts%20Question%20Outgoing%20administration's%20credibility%20point%20to%20DoJ's%20Vindictive%20Action%20against%20Adanis.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20the%20panel%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChellaney%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Chellaney%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20former%20diplomat%20Yogesh%20Gupta%20with%20NDTV's%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fv7k9jGlmOQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fv7k9jGlmOQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1863487076790063328%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden's%20move%20has%20also%20raised%20serious%20questions%20over%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20action%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20There%20is%20a%20wider%20feeling%20among%20diplomats%20that%20the%20Adani%20indictment%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20is%20also%20politically%20driven%20by%20the%20outgoing%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20President's%20son%20Hunter%20Biden%20was%20found%20guilty%20and%20convicted%20of%20his%20charges%2C%20there%20has%20not%20been%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20against%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Sagar%20Adani%20and%20senior%20executive%20Vneet%20Jaain%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20by%20the%20DoJ%20and%20SEC%2C%20suspected%20of%20acting%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20and%20the%20SEC%20had%20filed%20an%20indictment%20and%20a%20civil%20complaint%20in%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20against%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Sagar%20Adani%2C%20and%20Vneet%20Jaain%2C%20key%20executives%20of%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%20(AGEL).%20The%20Adani%20Group%20had%20rejected%20the%20allegations%2C%20terming%20it%20totally%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20it%20would%20seek%20legal%20recourse%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinding%20itself%20on%20the%20back-foot%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20evidence%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20in%20a%20recent%20public%20statement%20in%20the%20Adani%20case%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20are%20always%20innocent%20unless%20and%20until%20proven%20guilty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden's%20move%20today%20has%20sparked%20off%20a%20fierce%20debate%20in%20the%20United%20States's%20power%20corridors%20on%20whether%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20is%20indeed%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%26quot%3B%20by%20political%20powerhouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20NEW%20FBI%20DIRECTOR%20'KASH'%20PATEL%20SAID%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashyap%20Patel%2C%20lawyer%2C%20investigator%20and%20a%20stern%20critic%20of%20the%20US%20deep%20state%2C%20has%20spoken%20out%20openly%20about%20%26quot%3Bpartisan%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B%20practices%20and%20also%20called%20for%20a%20