security%20concerns.%20With%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20resolve%20the%20deadlock%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20a%20'hybrid'%20formula%20was%20floated%20that%20meant%20India%20will%20be%20playing%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai.%20Several%20media%20reports%20suggested%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20was%20ready%20to%20accept%20it%20if%20the%20ICC%20was%20willing%20to%20give%20a%20written%20confirmation%20that%20all%20Pakistan%20matches%20in%20events%20hosted%20by%20India%20will%20take%20place%20in%20a%20neutral%20venue%20and%20they%20are%20given%20an%20increase%20share%20in%20annual%20revenue.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcricketpakistan.com.pk%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Findia-objects-to-proposed-formula-for-champions-trophy-2025-final%5C%22%3ECricketPakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BCCI%20is%20'hesitant'%20in%20accepting%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20ICC%20agrees%20to%20Pakistan's%20conditions%2C%20the%20final%20of%20future%20competitions%20will%20have%20to%20be%20moved%20out%20of%20India%20in%20case%20Pakistan%20ended%20up%20qualifying%20for%20the%20summit%20clash.%20The%20report%20believes%20that%20is%20an%20issue%20for%20BCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20presented%20a%20fair%20solution.%20If%20India%20does%20not%20accept%20it%2C%20they%20cannot%20expect%20us%20to%20send%20our%20team%20there%20in%20the%20future.%20If%20an%20ICC%20event%20is%20held%20in%20India%2C%20their%20team%20would%20also%20need%20to%20play%20finals%20or%20key%20matches%20in%20Dubai%2C%20ensuring%20parity%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20PCB%20source%20was%20quoted%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20uncertainty%20looming%20over%20the%20future%20of%20ICC%C2%A0Champions%C2%A0Trophy%C2%A02025%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20stated%20that%20hosting%20the%20tournament%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20is%20%26quot%3Bde