%20said%20no%20one%20is%20ready%20to%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20to%20jobless%20men.%20She%20also%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20we%20rabbits%20that%20we%20will%20keep%20reproducing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20at%20Parliament%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20unemployed%20men%20in%20the%20country%20cannot%20get%20married%20because%20no%20one%20is%20willing%20to%20fix%20their%20daughters'%20wedding%20with%20a%20jobless%20man.%20They%20don't%20have%20jobs.%20How%20will%20they%20take%20care%20(of%20their%20partners)%3F%20There%20is%20no%20money.%20Elderly%20parents%20are%20working%20and%20looking%20after%20their%20children.%20And%20he%20is%20saying%20produce%20more%20children.%20Are%20we%20rabbits%20that%20we%20will%20keep%20reproducing%3F%20Those%20who%20are%20talking%2C%20how%20many%20children%20can%20they%20bring%20up%3F%20What%20is%20their%20experience%3F%20We%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20pointed%20to%20adulteration%20in%20food%20items%2C%20price%20rise%20of%20essential%20items%20and%20rising%20travel%20costs.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20gets%20sick%20and%20is%20hospitalised%2C%20the%20treatment%20costs%20are%20huge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20was%20responding%20to%20Mr%20Bhagwat's%20remarks%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Nagpur%20yesterday.%20The%20RSS%20chief%20said%20that%20the%20country's%20declining%20population%20is%20a%20serious%20concern.%20%26quot%3BDemographic%20studies%20suggest%20that%20when%20a%20society's%20total%20fertility%20rate%20falls%20below%202.1%2C%20it%20risks%20facing%20extinction.%20This%20decline%20does%20not%20necessarily%20require%20external%20threats%3B%20a%20society%20can%20gradually%20fade%20away%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20languages%20and%20cultures%20have%20already%20disappeared%20due%20to%20this%20issue.%20Thus%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20maintain%20a%20fertility%20rate%20above%202.1%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20said.%20He%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bkutumb%26quot%3B%20(family)%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20society%20and%20every%20family%20serves%20as%20a%20vital%20building%20bloc%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20country's%20population%20policy%2C%20formulated%20either%20in%201998%20or%202002%2C%20clearly%20says%20that%20the%20total%20fertility%20rate%20should%20not%20be%20below%202.1.%20Now%20when%20we%20say%202.1%2C%20it%20is%20not%20feasible%20to%20have%20children%20in%20fraction.%20So%20when%20we%20say%202.1%2C%20this%20means%20it%20should%20be%20more%2C%20at%20least%20three.%20The%20(population)%20science%20says%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RSS%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Total%20Fertility%20Rate%2C%20a%20key%20indicator%20to%20track%20the%20country's%20population%20change%2C%20has%20declined%20from%202.2%20to%202.%20A%20TFR%20less%20than%202.1%20indicates%20that%20the%20population%20is%20shrinking%20and%20the%20median%20age%20is%20increasing.%20This%20points%20to%20an%20aging%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733140200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fq5uckh1g_renuka-chowdhury_625x300_02_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frenuka-chowdhury-mohan-bhagwat-are-we-rabbits-congress-mp-on-mohan-bhagwats-three-children-advice-7154654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20snappy%20response%20to%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20remarks%20on%20India's%20declining%20population%20growth%20and%20his%20advice%20to%20every%20couple%20to%20produce%20at%20least%20three%20children%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Renuka%20Chowdhury%20pointed%20to%20unemployment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frenuka-chowdhury-mohan-bhagwat-are-we-rabbits-congress-mp-on-mohan-bhagwats-three-children-advice-7154654%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22