ice%2C%20Bolt%2C%20has%20expanded%20to%20over%20400%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20including%20tier-2%20and%20tier-3%20locations.%20Popular%20cities%20for%20the%20service%20include%20Jaipur%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20Coimbatore.%20Swiggy%20has%20partnered%20with%20renowned%20restaurant%20chains%20to%20offer%20diverse%20menus%2C%20aiming%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20rapid%20food%20delivery%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Case%2C%20Court%20Commissioners%20Claim%20Threat%2C%20Bench%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20Delhi%20and%20other%20National%20Capital%20Region%20states%20for%20not%20paying%20an%20allowance%20to%20labourers%20after%20construction%20activities%20were%20halted%20due%20to%20air%20pollution%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20it%20has%20seen%20that%20the%20ball%20starts%20rolling%20only%20when%20it%20summons%20top%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20find%20that%20none%20of%20the%20NCR%20States%20have%20complied%20with%20our%20direction%20to%20pay%20compensation%20to%20construction%20workers.%20Not%20even%20proof%20of%20a%20penny%20being%20paid%20has%20been%20shown.%20We%20order%20the%20Chief%20Secretaries%20to%20be%20present%20on%20VC%20(video%20conference).%20Let%20them%20come%2C%20then%20they%20will%20be%20serious.%20We%20want%20proof%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20AG%20Masih%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20experience%20that%20the%20ball%20starts%20rolling%20only%20when%20we%20summon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20had%20expected%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20states%20to%20show%20that%20they%20had%20paid%20the%20allowance%20to%20a%20sizeable%20number%20of%20workers.%20The%20Chief%20Secretaries%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20refused%20to%20relax%20the%20curbs%20imposed%20under%20Stage%204%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20to%20tackle%20the%20worsening%20Air%20Quality%20Index%2C%20which%20had%20entered%20the%20'severe%20%2B'%20band%20but%20has%20now%20dropped%20to%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20The%20bench%20said%20it%20would%20allow%20further%20relaxations%20only%20in%20case%20of%20a%20downward%20trend%20in%20AQI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bvery%20shocking%20things%26quot%3B%20are%20revealed%20in%20the%20reports%20of%20court%20commissions%20--%20members%20of%20the%20Bar%20asked%20by%20the%20court%20to%20monitor%20the%20implementation%20of%20curbs%20in%20NCR.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20complete%20lack%20of%20coordination%20between%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20MCD%20(Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%2C%20DPCC%20(Delhi%20Pollution%20Control%20Committee)%2C%20CAQM%20(Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management)%20and%20other%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20lawyer%20said%20that%20the%20court%20commissioners%20are%20being%20intimidated.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20feeling%20very%20unsafe.%20Local%20toll%20persons%20and%20SHO%20told%20me%20this%20area%20is%20of%20big%20shooters%2C%20criminals%20and%20all%2C%20and%20gang%20and%20muscle%20people%20are%20very%20active%20here%20and%20not%20paying%20toll.%20This%20is%20ground%20reality%20and%20live%20stubble%20burning%20is%20also%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20court%20commissioner%20advocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20in%20its%20order%20that%20it%20commends%20the%20work%20of%20court%20commissioners.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20stated%20that%20they%20have%20risked%20their%20lives%20in%20their%20duty.%20We%20direct%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20file%20a%20report%20in%20this%20court%20setting%20out%20action%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20commissioners%20can%20also%20seek%20armed%20protection%20from%20Delhi%20Police.%20%26quot%3BWe%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20ensure%20that%20members%20of%20the%20Bar%20who%20are%20court%20commissioners%20are%20adequately%20protected%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20counsel%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%20told%20the%20court%20that%20GRAP%20curbs%20are%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20disruptive%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20the%20court%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20clear%20downward%20trend%20how%20can%20we%20relax%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20bench%20also%20blasted%20a%20lawyer%20who%20pointed%20out%20that%20no%20masks%20were%20being%20distributed.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20us%20to%20run%20the%20government.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20some%20limit.%20If%20you%20want%20us%20to%20turn%20tell%20the%20CJI%20to%20make%20us%20hear%20only%20this%20and%20leave%20other%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20allowed%20Delhi%20government%20to%20repair%20sewage%20lines%20and%20roads%20that%20are%20in%20dire%20condition.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20not%20a%20single%20vehicle%20shall%20be%20used%20for%20this%20purpose%20which%20is%20not%20permissible%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733138880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fajaqgeq8_delhi-air-pollution_625x300_28_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-supreme-court-grap-4-stays-supreme-court-flags-no-coordination-in-delhi-pollution-fight-7154266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coming%20down%20heavily%20on%20Delhi%20and%20other%20NCR%20states%20for%20not%20paying%20an%20allowance%20to%20labourers%20after%20construction%