0Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20have%20agreed%20to%20hold%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20Constitution%20next%20week%2C%20days%20after%20chaotic%20sessions%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20came%20today%20after%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20with%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20on%20the%20Constitution%20will%20be%20held%20on%20December%2013%20and%2014%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%2016%20and%2017%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20told%20reporters%20outside%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20good%20to%20disrupt%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%20We%20appeal%20to%20all%20Opposition%20leaders%20to%20make%20good%20on%20the%20agreement%20that%20all%20of%20us%20will%20ensure%20parliament%20functions%20smoothly%20from%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20session%20of%20parliament's%20winter%20session%20began%20on%20November%2025%2C%20with%20both%20houses%20getting%20adjourned%20fairly%20early%20due%20to%20disruptions.%20The%20session%20will%20go%20on%20till%20December%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20had%20demanded%20discussions%20in%20both%20houses%20to%20mark%20the%2075th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20by%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20has%20been%20fending%20off%20Opposition%20attacks%20that%20Modi%203.0%20would%20tinker%20with%20the%20Constitution.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20more%20than%20once%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20claims%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20got%20a%20singular%20majority%20again%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20the%20mandate%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20but%20we%20never%20did%20that.%20What%20do%20you%20think%20Rahul%20Baba%20and%20company%20would%20say%2C%20and%20the%20country%20will%20believe%20it%3F%20This%20country%20has%20given%20us%20a%20clear%20mandate%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20already%20know%20that%20Modi%20ji%20already%20had%20sufficient%20majority%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%2C%20but%20we%20never%20did%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20had%20said%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju's%20recent%20comments%20at%20an%20event%20to%20announce%20programmes%20linked%20to%20the%20Constitution%20Day%20celebrations%20on%20November%2026%2C%20however%2C%20have%20prompted%20the%20Opposition%20to%20take%20note%20again.%20The%20Constitution%20is%20not%20only%20a%20static%20document%20but%20a%20journey%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20amended%20before%2C%20Mr%20Riiju%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20India%20Samvad%20Samvidhan%202024%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20is%20a%20book.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20citizen%2C%20we%20have%20to%20follow%20a%20way%20of%20life.%20Many%20people%20have%20given%20their%20views%20on%20the%20Constitution%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20and%20they%20are%20constructive%20views.%20People%20have%20also%20looked%20at%20the%20Constitution%20with%20different%20views%20at%20different%20points%20of%20time%2C%20amendments%20have%20been%20made%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Parliamentary%20and%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20going%20into%20minute%20details%20about%20the%20Constitution%20as%20it%20will%20be%20a%20lengthy%20discussion.%20But%20everyone%20knows%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20not%20a%20static%20document.%20It%20is%20a%20journey%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20changes%20and%20will%20see%20changes.%20Except%20for%20the%20basic%20principles%20which%20are%20at%20the%20core%2C%20which%20we%20cannot%20and%20should%20not%20touch%2C%20nothing%20is%20permanent%20in%20a%20democratic%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Opposition%20raising%20other%20issues%20such%20a