ory%20of%20the%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20K-4%20missile%20was%20reportedly%20tested%20from%20submarine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-gets-its-second-nuclear-submarine-ins-arighat-6445867%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EINS%20Arighaat%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20which%20was%20commissioned%20into%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20on%20August%2029%20-%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Visakhapatnam%20on%20November%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20it%20was%20the%20first%20test%20of%20the%20submarine-launched%20ballistic%20missile%20(SLBM)%20from%20a%20submarine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-successfully-tests-nuclear-capable-ballistic-missile-launched-from-submarine-7124728%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EK-4%20missile%20test%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20also%20became%20part%20of%20a%20small%20group%20of%20countries%20that%20can%20fire%20a%20nuclear%20missile%20from%20land%2C%20air%20and%20undersea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20significantly%20enhanced%20its%20overall%20military%20capabilities%20and%20test-fired%20a%20range%20of%20missiles%20with%20varying%20ranges%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Tripathi%20also%20said%20the%20government's%20approval%20for%20two%20SSNs%20(nuclear-powered%20attack%20submarines)%20indicated%20its%20%26quot%3Bfaith%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country's%20indigenous%20capabilities%20to%20build%20such%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20attack%20submarines%20are%20used%20to%20target%20enemy%20ships%20and%20submarines%20and%20may%20launch%20cruise%20missiles%20against%20land%20and%20sea%20targets.%20These%20are%20different%20from%20SSBMs%20such%20as%20the%20INS%20Arighaat%2C%20which%20have%20a%20primary%20role%20of%20launching%20nuclear-tipped%20ballistic%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Tripathi%20said%2062%20ships%20and%20a%20submarine%20are%20currently%20under%20construction%20within%20the%20country%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20boost%20its%20naval%20power.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20platforms%20are%20waiting%20for%20induction%20in%20the%20next%20one%20year%20and%20at%20least%20one%20ship%20will%20be%20inducted%20into%20the%20Navy%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20redoubled%20efforts%20to%20include%20niche%20technologies%20into%20the%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Navy%20Chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20procurement%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-submits-final-price-offer-to-india-for-26-rafale-marine-jet-deal-6677687%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERafale-M%3C%2Fa%3E%20(naval%20variant)%20and%20the%20Scorpene%20submarines%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20finalised%20next%20month.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20defence%20ministry%20approved%20the%20purchase%20of%20the%20Rafale-M%20jets%20from%20France%2C%20primarily%20for%20deployment%20on%20board%20the%20indigenously%20built%20aircraft%20carrier%20INS%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Tripathi%20also%20said%20they%20have%20kept%20a%20%26quot%3Bclose%20watch%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20activities%20of%20extra-regional%20forces%20operating%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%20including%20the%20Chinese%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20is%20their%20warships%20or%20their%20research%20vessels%2C%20we%20know%20who%20is%20doing%20what%2C%20where%20and%20how%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20they%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurprising%20growth%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Navy%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20become%20a%2050-ship%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20chosen%20weapons%20over%20the%20welfare%20of%20their%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733129880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F7rrkr6co_navy-chief-admiral-dinesh-k-tripathi_625x300_02_December_24.jpeg%22