2C%20two%20young%20men%20in%20Ahmedabad%20died%20when%20a%20speeding%20Hyundai%20Creta%20jumped%20the%20road%20divider%20and%20crashed%20into%20a%20scooter%20in%20the%20next%20lane.%20The%20killer%20accident%20was%20captured%20by%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20overlooking%20the%20road.%20The%20driver%2C%20Gopal%20Patel%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20police%20have%20said%20he%20was%20drunk%20driving.%20He%20has%20been%20charged%20in%20a%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Naroda-Dehgam%20road%20in%20Ahmedabad%20last%20night.%20Footage%20from%20the%20CCTV%20camera%20shows%20an%20auto-rikshaw%20and%20Hyundai%20Creta%20SUV%20behind%20it.%20The%20SUV%20driver%20overtakes%20the%20three-wheeler%20at%20high%20speed%2C%20but%20loses%20control%2C%20and%20jumps%20the%20divider%20into%20the%20next%20lane.%20The%20SUV%20was%20in%20the%20air%20for%20at%20least%20five%20seconds%20and%20was%20tilted%20to%20one%20side%2C%20suggesting%20the%20speed%20it%20was%20in.%20As%20it%20lands%2C%20it%20crashes%20into%20a%20Honda%20Activa%20scooter%20coming%20from%20the%20opposite%20side.%20Amit%20Rathore%20(26)%20and%20Vishal%20Rathore%20(27)%2C%20who%20were%20on%20the%20scooter%2C%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fsfpposr8_gujarat-accident_625x300_02_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20and%20passersby%20thrashed%20the%20SUV's%20driver%20after%20the%20killer%20crash%20and%20then%20handed%20him%20over%20to%20the%20police.%20Ahmedabad%20rural%20police%20chief%20Om%20Prakash%20Jat%20has%20said%20Gopal%20Patel%20was%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident.%20%26quot%3BPolice%20have%20arrested%20the%20accused.%20A%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20has%20been%20registered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20last%20year%2C%20India%20reported%20over%204.61%20lakh%20accidents%20in%202022%20and%20over%201.68%20lakh%20people%20died%20in%20road%20crashes.%20This%20translates%20to%20over%20450%20deaths%20due%20to%20accidents%20every%20day.%20Nearly%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20under%2045.%20Over%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20accidents%20and%20over%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20deaths%20were%20due%20to%20'over%20speeding'.%20Drunked%20driving%2C%20jumping%20red%20light%2C%20driving%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20and%20the%20use%20of%20mobile%20phones%20were%20the%20other%20major%20causes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInputs%20by%20Mahendra%20Prasad%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733128920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F4snnlt4_guj-accident_625x300_02_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcreta-suv-driven-by-drunk-man-jumps-divider-crashes-into-scooter-2-dead-7153624%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20case%20of%20innocents%20paying%20the%20price%20of%20a%20rash%20driver's%20negligence%2C%20two%20young%20men%20in%20Ahmedabad%20died%20when%20a%20speeding%20Hyundai%20Creta%20jumped%20the%20road%20divider%20and%20crashed%20into%20a%20scooter%20in%20the%20next%20lane%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcreta-suv-driven-by-drunk-man-jumps-divider-crashes-into-scooter-2-dead-7153624%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Abhishek%20Bachchan%20gave%20Shweta%20Bachchan%20a%20haircut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733128887000%2C%22visu