wp-image-383802%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Annual%20Status%20of%20Education%20Report%2C%2025%25%20of%20teens%20aged%2014-18%20struggle%20to%20read%20grade%202%20level%20text%20fluently.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20storyteller%20and%20writer%2C%20Srishti%20understands%20firsthand%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20books.%20%E2%80%9CStorybooks%20have%20impacted%20my%20life%20a%20lot%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up.%20My%20love%20for%20reading%20is%20the%20reason%20I%20was%20able%20to%20do%20something%20with%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20SABIA%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20help%20provide%20every%20child%20with%20access%20to%20books%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20comprehend%20them.%20In%202024%20alone%2C%20SABIA%20has%20extended%20its%20reach%20to%20over%2030%2C000%20children%20across%20175%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20community%20of%20readers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20UPSC%20aspirant%20and%20a%20voracious%20reader%2C%20Srishti%20was%20heavily%20invested%20in%20volunteer%20work.%20Recalling%20a%20conversation%20she%20had%20with%20a%20friend%20who%20had%20taken%20her%20house-help%E2%80%99s%20son%20to%20be%20admitted%20to%20a%20school%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act%2C%20Srishti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20friend%20mentioned%20that%20the%20children%20in%20that%20government%20school%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20library.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20place%20to%20read!%20That%20really%20stuck%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20product%20of%20a%20privileged%20education%20system%20where%20access%20to%20libraries%20was%20a%20given%2C%20many%20of%20us%20fail%20to%20consider%20that%20such%20a%20fundamental%20resource%20is%20missing%20for%20so%20many%20children.%20Srishti%20soon%20started%20a%20Facebook%20page%2C%20then%20moved%20to%20Instagram%20and%20formed%20a%20strong%20%E2%80%98Bookstagram%E2%80%99%20community%2C%20where%20she%20rallied%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20donate%20books.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20they%20found%20a%20group%20of%20people%20who%20really%20understood%20and%20empathised%20with%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20it%20grew%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20initiative%20that%20now%20includes%20a%20library%20development%20programme%20for%20rural%20and%20remote%20schools%2C%20a%20teacher%20training%20programme%2C%20book%20fairs%2C%20and%20donation%20drives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%20to%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20done%20by%20SABIA%20in%20March%202022%20revealed%20that%20over%2050%20government%20schools%20in%20Rajasthan%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20implement%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Padhe%20Bharat%20Badhe%20Bharat%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20government%20scheme%20which%20aims%20to%20provide%20extra%20reading%20material%20and%20inculcate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F207803%2Ftamil-nadu-barber-library-salon-discount-read-books-harsha-bhogle-viral-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20habit%20of%20reading%3C%2Fa%3E%20amongst%20the%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20even%20though%20there%20is%20a%20government%20scheme%20that%20wants%20to%20tackle%20this%20problem%20that%20has%20been%20identified%2C%20those%20books%20are%20never%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srishti.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20something%20that%20we%20have%20been%20working%20towards%20diligently.%20We%20are%20making%20all%20stakeholders%20within%20the%20school%20system%2C%20the%20teachers%2C%20and%20principals%20understand%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20if%20the%20books%20are%20used%20and%20damaged.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20pointless%20to%20even%20have%20them%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204110px)%20100vw%2C%204110px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224110%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20volunteer%20conducting%20a%20storytelling%20session%2C%20engaging%20a%20group%20of%20children%20with%20a%20lively%20narration.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104.jpg%204110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-17327